Name: Football Team Manager Match Participation
Description: Football Team Manager Match Participation links a Football Team Manager to the football matches in which they were present, and the team which they represented at the match.

Properties.Name: Match
Properties.Description: The match participated in by the manager

Properties.Name: Team
Properties.Description: The team represented by this manager at this match

Properties.Name: Manager
Properties.Description: The football (soccer) team manager present at the football match
